BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:gEQu96CUgSKNHMFHODIpl
SUMMARY:The Swapanistas Present: Swap! A Women's Clothing Exchange
DTSTAMP:20260308T063046Z
DTSTART:20260314T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you ready to swap up your style? \\nThen join us for Swap 2
	026! \\nSwap is an amazing event where you let go of your gently used clot
	hing and accessories and trade them in for items that make you feel brand 
	new\\\, while having fun and supporting a good cause: proceeds and clothin
	g donations benefit local organizations for underserved women and kids. \\
	nWe are excited to announce that this year’s event is being hosted in part
	nership with the Phinney Neighborhood Association\\\, truly making this a 
	community event! \\n​​Come check it out\\\, and bring your friends! \\nSwa
