DESCRIPTION:In this workshop with Angie Cooper of My Moon Macrame you will 
	be taught the basic knotting techniques used in macrame. This class is gre
	at for beginners and intermediate levels. This project is designed to be a
	ltered to cater to students at any skill level. We provide craft supplies\
	\\, video tutorials and one-on-one guidance to help you create your macram
	e project. \\nDuring this class you will learn to macrame a lanyard keycha
	in. Your instructor\\\, Angie from My Moon Macrame will teach you the knot
	s and provide step by step instructions to help you complete your project.
	 We provide all craft supplies\\\, video tutorials and one-on-one guidance
	. This project is designed to cater to students at any skill level. You wi
	ll go home with a completed macrame lanyard keychain and all the tools you
	 need to continue your macrame journey at home. \\nSupplies: \\n4mm Oeko T
	ex Recycled Cotton Cord\\nKey Ring\\nScissors\\nTape\n\nhttps://myballard.
