SUMMARY:The Crocodile Presents: Surf Hat\, Trestles
DTSTAMP:20260308T063046Z
DTSTART:20260626T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $20 ($28.33 after fees)\n\nDay of: $25 ($33.48 after f
	ees)\n\nSurf Hat:\n\nSurf Hat is the ever-evolving and fun-loving creative
	 brain child of the duo of Jon Allan and Evan Camm. A melting pot of surf\
	, psych\, folk\, and indie.\n\nBased out of the mountains of British Colum
	bia\, the group has released two full length albums since 2022 and perform
	ed relentlessly across western Canada. They are queuing up their third ful
	l length for fall 2025.\n\nPlease note\, the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 2
	1+ bar and venue and does not accept vertical ID’s for entry.\n\nhttps://l
	ink.dice.fm/fe4ea65bc46e\n\nFrom Sunset Tavern
